$interpreted: Pang: Out of sight, out of mind. Nowhere...where could he have possibly flown to?
Hestia: Help me! OH!
Pang: COMING!
Hestia: Deary me. Thank you, kind sir.
Hestia: Detestable wolves always attack the herbivores. You should have struck them dead like lightning.
Pang: Why have you caught such unsolicited attention?
Hestia: If it weren't for some, for some... RASCAL who kept provoking the wolves, I wouldn't be in this situation lest he couldn't make it out alive.
Pang: This "rascal"... what's he like?
Hestia: Er~ Well, he was a fat bird with itsy bitsy feet, crowned with a pair of horns that look a little like... croissants.
Hestia: Aha, that's him!
Puggi: Milady, are you alright?
Puggi: Swing batter batter, SAFE~ I could've taken on those wolves myself, I could feel it in my nuggets! But you all ran way outfield, what could I do——
Pang: Stop flying away from the nest, you cuckoo!
Puggi: PANG! Ya big guy, there you are. Where have you gone off to, I've been searching for so loooooong~
Pang: It was I who was on the birdhunt!
Puggi: Meh~ We know our way without a map anyways~
Pang: Stop playing fowl! And toss that banter of yours. If you ever leave my sight again, you're OUT!
Puggi: Hmph. The more you say that, the more I want to walk this way, in a zig zag! BEHIND YOU!
Pang: I am skilled in martial arts, with much flexibility too. There are eyes on the back of my head, you know.
Hestia: Puuhahahahaha~
Hestia: Haha~ Sorry, didn't mean to be rude. It's just that you both are so cute!
Hestia: My name is Hestia, and you both are?
Pang: Pang, from the East Alliance. The fat bird is Puggi.
Puggi: Hi there, Ms. Heartstopping Hestia~
Hestia: Oh, I see. What are you both doing in Maple Lake?
Pang: I have heard tales of a martial arts master, and seek forth to become his protege.
Hestia: Master... I suppose, you're looking for Yan-Bo?
Pang: You know him?! Could you introduce me formally?
Hestia: I could and maybe I would... Although, I don't think Yan-Bo's going to accept?
Pang: Not an issue. I am a bona fide novice willing to try anything! He wouldn't find it in his heart to turn someone as passionate as me down!
Hestia: Alright, this way then!
